step_data.thought:
I received a timeout error when trying to click on the 'Bicycle (OSRM)' option directly. This suggests that the option element itself isn't directly clickable, which is common for select/option elements. Instead, I should use the select_option method to select the bicycle option from the dropdown.

Looking at the accessibility tree, I can see:
- The combobox has ID 166 and is currently expanded
- The 'Bicycle (OSRM)' option has ID 167

I should use select_option on the combobox (ID 166) to select 'Bicycle (OSRM)'.
